The paper proposes a computational prediction method for detecting synthetic lethality in cancer cells. It employs logistic matrix factorization to learn latent representations of genes and incorporates biological knowledge from protein-protein interaction data and Gene Ontology. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
